{"synckey":1599840602,"updated":[{"bookId":"843312","bookmarkId":"843312_9_1850-1891","chapterUid":9,"markText":"竞争回报率下限，又称“自由市场回报率”，与扣除了资本损失风险的长期政府债券收益相当","range":"1850-1891","createTime":1599698372,"type":1},{"bookId":"843312","bookmarkId":"843312_9_1451-1476","chapterUid":9,"markText":"“产品”指代行业的产出，而没有用具体的产品或者服务","range":"1451-1476","createTime":1599698296,"type":1},{"bookId":"843312","bookmarkId":"843312_9_1631-1659","chapterUid":9,"markText":"行业定义为“由生产彼此可以替代的产品的企业组成的集合”。","range":"1631-1659","createTime":1599698279,"type":1},{"bookId":"843312","bookmarkId":"843312_9_1135-1200","chapterUid":9,"markText":"业务单元在某个行业内实施竞争战略的目标是在行业内寻找最佳的定位，让企业更好地维护自身的竞争力或者以有利于企业发展的方式影响竞争力。","range":"1135-1200","createTime":1599698079,"type":1},{"bookId":"843312","bookmarkId":"843312_9_774-840","chapterUid":9,"markText":"诸如轮胎、纸和钢材行业，竞争强度比较大，几乎没有企业能赢得可观的回报；在石油设备和服务、化妆品以及化妆用具行业，竞争强度则相对不大。","range":"774-840","createTime":1599698040,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"01 行业的结构化分析","chapterUid":9,"chapterIdx":9}],"book":{"bookId":"843312","version":1150580059,"format":"epub","soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/77/YueWen_843312/s_YueWen_843312.jpg","title":"竞争战略","author":"迈克尔·波特","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"K65EmdoL0esAfQSg4.WV^+","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#171d22"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#171d22"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#171d22"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#2c3236"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#2c3236"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#2c3236"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#41494e"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#41494e"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#41494e"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#41494e"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#5a6166"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#5a6166"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#5a6166"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#747b7f"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#747b7f"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#747b7f"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#8d9499"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#8d9499"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#8d9499"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#8d9499"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#a8afb2"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#a8afb2"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#a8afb2"},{"key":"8/4","hex"